                            "correctAnswer": "70.7",
                            "hint": "Usa la fórmula vertical: Fy = F * sen(theta). Reemplaza F = 100 y sen(45°) ≈ 0.707.",
                            "feedbackCorrect": "¡Excelente! Fy = 100 * 0.707 = 70.7 N.",
                            "feedbackIncorrect": "Incorrecto. Fy = 100 * sen(45°) = 70.7.",
                            "difficulty": "básico",
